             was indicted for <rs id="t18250915-309-off1672" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18250915-309-off1672" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18250915-309-off1672" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18250915-309-cd1673" type="crimeDate">11th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-309-off1672 t18250915-309-cd1673"></join>, a handkerchief, value 3 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250915-309-victim1560" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Gibbs
                     <interp inst="t18250915-309-victim1560" type="surname" value="Gibbs"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18250915-309-victim1560" type="given" value="John"></interp>
